    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Probability of class 'setosa': 0.9978\n",
      "Probability of class 'versicolor': 0.0022\n",
      "Probability of class 'virginica': 0.0000\n",
      "Accuracy score of the MLP model: 1.0\n",
      "Configuration: (1,) - Accuracy: 0.9333\n",
      "Configuration: (5,) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "Configuration: (10,) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "Configuration: (50,) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "Configuration: (100,) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "Configuration: (100, 50) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "Configuration: (150, 100) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "Configuration: (100, 100, 50) - Accuracy: 1.0000\n",
      "\n",
      "Best Configuration: (5,)\n",
      "Best Accuracy Score: 1.0\n",
      "From this experiment, I discovered that for a maximum number of iterations of 10000 the best configuration is (5, ) with 5 hidden layers.\n",
